<lyrics>[V1]
 ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb ḥmlt ʿạry fyh ạftkẖạry
 ạ̹nt ạ̹lhy ạ̹nt ḥbyby wmkẖlṣy
 ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb ṣrt sẖfạyạ
 mn ạlkẖṭạyạ wạlẓrwf wmn ạlʿywb ạlly ṣạbt
 jwh ạlqlwb
 ạ̹nt rḍyt ttjld ʿlsẖạn tsẖfyny
 ạ̹nt rḍyt ttṣlb wtmwt ʿlsẖạn tḥyyny
 ạ̉nạ msẖ hạbṣ wrạyạ whạdws ʿly̱ ạlkẖṭạyạ
 wbqwẗ dmk ly nṣrẗ wly ḥyạẗ
 wlạ hạsmḥ lʿdwy yjyy fy ywm yksrny
 wlạ yṭrḥ ạlʿmr ạlly rby ạftdạh
 fy ạlṣlyb rfʿt rạsy ạ̹nt kẖlạṣy yạ sydy</lyrics>
<title>ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb</title>
</song>